      "source": [
        "pressure = df.dropna(subset=[\"Date\"]).copy()\n",
        "if \"Season\" not in pressure.columns:\n",
        "    season_year = np.where(pressure[\"Date\"].dt.month >= 7, pressure[\"Date\"].dt.year, pressure[\"Date\"].dt.year - 1)\n",
        "    pressure[\"Season\"] = season_year.astype(str)\n",
        "\n",
        "pressure = pressure.sort_values([\"Season\", \"Date\"]).copy()\n",
        "pressure[\"idx\"] = pressure.groupby(\"Season\").cumcount() + 1\n",
        "pressure[\"season_total\"] = pressure.groupby(\"Season\")[\"idx\"].transform(\"max\")\n",
        "pressure[\"progress\"] = pressure[\"idx\"] / pressure[\"season_total\"]\n",
        "pressure[\"phase\"] = np.where(pressure[\"progress\"] >= 0.75, \"late\", \"earlier\")\n",
        "\n",
        "phase_mix = pd.crosstab(pressure[\"phase\"], pressure[\"Result\"], normalize=\"index\").round(3)\n",
        "display(phase_mix)\n",
        "display(pressure.groupby(\"phase\")[[\"xG\", \"xGA\", \"Scored\", \"Conceded\"]].mean().round(3))\n",
        "\n",
        "phase_mix.plot(kind=\"bar\", figsize=(8, 4))\n",
        "plt.title(\"Result Mix: Late Season vs Earlier\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Proportion\")\n",
        "plt.tight_layout()\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "cef89271",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**Insight:** Late-season matches (final 25%) produce more draws (~27% vs ~24% earlier). Teams play more cautiously under end-of-season pressure — a season-phase flag could help the model."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "5950b8b2",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 11) Correlation of Key Match Features\n",
        "\n",
        "**Description:** See how core numeric features move together (correlation, not causation)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 35,
      "id": "cf531845",
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "image/png": "",
